snippet: Andy Murray won the China Open in Beijing on Sunday, defeating Grigor Dimitrov 6-4, 7-6 (2), in a hard-fought match that featured plenty of acrobatics from both players....
lead_paragraph: Andy Murray won the China Open in Beijing on Sunday, defeating Grigor Dimitrov 6-4, 7-6 (2), in a hard-fought match that featured plenty of acrobatics from both players.

headline.print_headline: Andy Murray Defeats Grigor Dimitrov to Win China Open
headline.main: Andy Murray Defeats Grigor Dimitrov to Win China Open
